(65, 1, '2019-08-06 22:52:58', '2019-08-07 03:52:58', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true} -->\n<p>Hey there! I\'m Danish Naseem and this is my blog. Simple as that haha. Don\'t worry there\'ll be plenty more posts. Each one being better than the previous. Now I know what y\'all might be thinking. What the heck is this blog even about. Well, the answer to that is short but vague.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p><strong>Answer:</strong> <em>Anything.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yup, that is right, this blog can be about anything we want. And to start off, I will be blogging about my college. The day-to-day life, the fun activities, the goofy shenanigans, all of it. Ok, maybe not all of it. But you get the point.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Oh yeah, I forgot to tell you about me. Who am I? Well, other than my name that is, I am just a normal day to day guy, living his normal day to day life. I am majoring in computer science, with music minor, recently just build my own website using html, css, javascript, bootstrap at <a href=\"https://danishnaseemoid.com/\">https://danishnaseemoid.com/</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>And yes, just as the domain of this blog states, this blog is part of that website. And making the site has opened my mind. It went:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:quote {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\n<blockquote style=\"text-align:left\"><p><em>Hey why not try blogging. You have some silly some fun, and some interesting ideas, why not let the world see them through your writing, pictures, videos, or whatever form of media there is to be shared with.</em></p><cite>My Brain</cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So, here I am writing this first post about to embark on my unforeseen journey. I might come back to this very blog in the future and laugh at what a rookie I was. But we never know haha!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Welcome!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-autosave-v1', '', '', '2019-08-06 22:52:58', '2019-08-07 03:52:58', '', 10, 'https://blog.danishnaseemoid.com/blog/2019/08/06/10-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
