(168, 1, '2019-08-28 23:26:02', '2019-08-29 04:26:02', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true,\"textColor\":\"very-dark-gray\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-background has-drop-cap has-very-dark-gray-color has-very-light-gray-background-color\">\n\nThis audacious Summer of 2019 began with a couple of friends and I purchasing our memberships to hit the thrilling rides and the wet slippery slides of the Six Flags Great America. The park itself is in fact amusing, but with the people as daring as us however makes it more enticing.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\">\n\nNow, enough of that. Let\'s dive into it then shall we haha.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\">The first day was quite the adventure, even though we only got to go on a few rides, as due to them long long lines. And I when I say long, I do mean LOOOOONG. But anyway, it was still a pretty fun day. One of the rides we went on was the Raging Bull. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":121,\"align\":\"left\",\"width\":249,\"height\":512} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft is-resized\"><img src=\"https://blog.danishnaseemoid.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Snapchat-1778572357-498x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Raging Bull\" class=\"wp-image-121\" width=\"249\" height=\"512\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true,\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-background has-drop-cap has-very-light-gray-background-color\">Here one of my friends and his girlfriend (let\'s call them <em><strong>Mr and Mrs. Frisky</strong></em>) stood in line adjacent from my other friend (let\'s call him the <em><strong>Water-Paranoia</strong></em>) and I. Mr frisky being the nice and energetic person he is, kept pissing mrs. frisky off by giving up their spot in line to other people, so that he could go on the ride at the same time as water-paranoia and I. Oh mr. frisky what\'re we ever gonna do about you smh. Well, this led to a whimsical of a conversation, where we all started roasting mr. frisky and saying, how mrs. frisky should\'ve left him at home and went on all the rides by herself. But mr. frisky wasn\'t the only one who got ridiculed. We would occasionally pretend to let other people ahead of us, just to see mrs frisky reaction, which might I say was pretty amusing considering the fact that we were standing in lines for who knows how long. But once we got on the rides, it was all worth it in the end. From the buildup of the ride slowly making its way to the top, to the screaming of it making its way down the drop (where by the way mrs. frisky would throw her hands in the air, even after being told again and again not to by the management. Something about life being too short she would say) was all worth it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true,\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-background has-drop-cap has-very-light-gray-background-color\">Moving on, a few rides later, we came across some water log rides, where now the infamous water-paranoia accidently \"joked\" about how he hates getting wet.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"customBackgroundColor\":\"#0c51e9\"} -->\n<p style=\"background-color:#0c51e9\" class=\"has-text-color has-background has-very-light-gray-color\"><em>And this is where he came to be known as \"Water-Paranoia\".</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\">He quickly regretted his words, as he was made to take the front seat. Lets just say, he wasn\'t the most driest by the time we left the park.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\">In case you are wondering, no we are not rude to each other, rather that is our way of living in the present. Even if it means standing in those LOOOONG ass lines, we would find a way to making them less boring.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"has-text-color has-luminous-vivid-orange-color has-custom-weight\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-luminous-vivid-orange-color has-custom-weight\"><em>To Be Continued ... </em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'My Summer 2K19 Six Flags', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '147-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-08-28 23:26:02', '2019-08-29 04:26:02', '', 147, 'https://blog.danishnaseemoid.com/blog/2019/08/28/147-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
