oasting mr. frisky and saying, how mrs. frisky should\'ve left him at home and went on all the rides by herself. But mr. frisky wasn\'t the only one who got ridiculed. We would occasionally pretend to let other people ahead of us, just to see mrs frisky reaction, which might I say was pretty amusing considering the fact that we were standing in lines for who knows how long. But once we got on the rides, it was all worth it in the end. From the buildup of the ride slowly making its way to the top, to the screaming of it making its way down the drop (where by the way mrs. frisky would throw her hands in the air, even after being told again and again not to by the management. Something about life being too short she would say) was all worth it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true,\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-background has-drop-cap has-very-light-gray-background-color\">But moving on, a few rides later, we came across some water log rides, where now the infamous water-paranoia accidently \"joked\" about how he hates getting wet.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"customBackgroundColor\":\"#1378e4\"} -->\n<p style=\"background-color:#1378e4\" class=\"has-text-color has-background has-very-light-gray-color\"><em><strong>And this is where he came to be known as \"Water-Paranoia\".</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\">He quickly regretted his words, as he was made to take the front seat. Lets just say, he wasn\'t the most driest by the time we left the park.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"dropCap\":true,\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-background has-drop-cap has-very-light-gray-background-color\">In case you are wondering, no we not mean, rather that is our way of enjoying the present. Even if it means standing in those LOOOONG ass lines, we would find a way to making them less boring.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:coblocks/alert {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-dark-gray\",\"textColor\":\"luminous-vivid-orange\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-coblocks-alert is-default-alert has-text-color has-luminous-vivid-orange-color has-background has-very-dark-gray-background-color\"><p class=\"wp-block-coblocks-alert__text\"><em><strong>To Be Continued ... </strong></em></p></div>\n<!-- /wp:coblocks/alert -->', 'My Summer 2K19 Six Flags', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '147-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-08-28 22:33:09', '2019-08-29 03:33:09', '', 147, 'https://blog.danishnaseemoid.com/blog/2019/08/28/147-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
