seat. Lets just say, he wasn\'t the most driest by the time we left the park.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\">In case you are wondering, no we not mean, rather that is our way of enjoying the present. Even if it means standing in those LOOOONG ass lines, we would find a way to making them less boring.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"textColor\":\"luminous-vivid-orange\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-dark-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-text-color has-background has-luminous-vivid-orange-color has-very-dark-gray-background-color\"><em><strong>To Be Continued ... </strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'My Summer 2K19 Six Flags', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '147-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-08-28 22:55:02', '2019-08-29 03:55:02', '', 147, 'https://blog.danishnaseemoid.com/blog/2019/08/28/147-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
